OL,3,CChild and three adults injured in
OL,4,Csuspected dog attack
OL,6,FA four-year-old child and three adults
OL,7,Fhave been injured in a suspected dog
OL,8,Fattack on Teesside.
OL,10,FA Malinois dog is reported to have
OL,11,Fattacked four people in the Brambles
OL,12,FFarm area of Middlesbrough on Sunday,
OL,13,F10 May.
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to
OL,16,FMarshall Avenue at about 2:10pm.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/5
