CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778746040
OL,3,CChild and three adults injured in
OL,4,Csuspected dog attack
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy, a 34-year-old man
OL,7,Fand a 36-year-old woman have been
OL,8,Farrested on suspicion of being in
OL,9,Fcharge of a dog dangerously out of
OL,10,Fcontrol causing injury. They have been
OL,11,Freleased on conditional bail.
OL,13,FOfficers have seized the dog while the
OL,14,Finvestigation into the incident is
OL,15,Fongoing.
OL,17,FThe child and three adults have all
OL,18,Freceived treatment in hospital for non-
OL,19,Flife-threatening injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/5
