OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1778746040
OL,3,CChild and three adults injured in
OL,4,Csuspected dog attack
OL,6,FTemporary Inspector Mike Dalton, from
OL,7,FCleveland Police's Middlesbrough
OL,8,Fresponse, said "officers swiftly
OL,9,Fattended to the area and the dog was
OL,10,Flocated and seized" following the
OL,11,Freport.
OL,13,FHe also urged anyone with information
OL,14,Fto contact the force.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
