OL,3,CChild and three adults injured in
OL,4,Csuspected dog attack
OL,6,F"I want to take this opportunity to
OL,7,Fappeal to anyone who has information
OL,8,For footage in the run to and during
OL,9,Fthe bite to please get in touch by
OL,10,Fcalling 101 or visiting the website
OL,11,Fquoting reference number 088568," he
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,F"If residents have concerns, I
OL,15,Fencourage you to please speak to an
OL,16,Fofficer."
